\c 11
\s UJesu ufundisa ngokukhuleka
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi ekhuleka endaweni ethile\x + 6.12.\x*, eseqedile, omunye wabafundi bakhe wathi kuye: Nkosi, sifundise ukukhuleka, njengoJohane laye wafundisa abafundi bakhe.
\v 2 Wasesithi kubo: Nxa likhuleka, libokuthi: Baba wethu osemazulwini, kalihlonitshwe ibizo lakho. Umbuso wakho kawuze. Intando yakho kayenziwe, lemhlabeni njengezulwini.
\v 3 Siphe usuku ngosuku ukudla kwethu kwensuku zonke.
\v 4 Njalo usithethelele izono zethu, ngoba lathi sibathethelela bonke abalamacala kithi. Njalo ungasingenisi ekulingweni, kodwa usikhulule ebubini\x + Mat. 6.9-13.\x*.
\s Umfanekiso womngane ofika phakathi kobusuku
\p
\v 5 Wasesithi kubo: Nguwuphi kini olomngane, futhi aye kuye phakathi kobusuku\x + Mark. 13.35.\x*, athi kuye: Mngane, ngeboleka izinkwa ezintathu,
\v 6 ngoba kufike kimi umngane wami evela ekuhambeni, kodwa kangilalutho engingalubeka phambi kwakhe\x + 10.8.\x*;
\v 7 longaphakathi aphendule athi: Ungangihluphi; umnyango usuvaliwe, labantwana bami abancane balami embhedeni; kangingeke ngivuke ngikunike.
\v 8 Ngithi kini: Loba engazukuvuka amnike, ngoba engumngane wakhe, kodwa ngenxa yokuphikelela kwakhe uzavuka amnike konke akuswelayo\x + 18.1-6.\x*.
\v 9 Mina-ke ngithi kini: Celani, lizaphiwa; dingani, lizathola; qoqodani, lizavulelwa.
\v 10 Ngoba wonke ocelayo uyemukela; lodingayo uyathola; loqoqodayo uyavulelwa\x + Mat. 7.7-11.\x*.
\v 11 Kambe, nguwuphi kini onguyise ongathi indodana icela isinkwa, ayinike ilitshe? Loba-ke inhlanzi, ayinike inyoka endaweni yenhlanzi yini?
\v 12 Uba-ke icela iqanda, ayinike ufezela yini\x + Dute. 8.15. 1 Kho. 12.11,14. 2 Lan. 10.11,14. Hez. 2.6. Luka 10.19. Isam. 9.3,5,10.\x*?
\v 13 Ngakho uba lina elingababi likwazi ukupha abantwana benu izipho ezinhle, kakhulu kangakanani uBaba osezulwini\x + 18.7,8.\x* ezabapha uMoya oNgcwele abacela kuye\x + Mat. 7.11.\x*.
\s Isono sokuhlambaza
\p
\v 14 Wayesekhupha idimoni, elaliyisimungulu. Kwasekusithi, seliphumile idimoni, wakhuluma oyisimungulu; amaxuku asemangala.
\v 15 Kodwa abanye babo bathi: Ukhupha amadimoni ngoBhelezebhule inkosi yamadimoni\x + 11.14,15, Mat. 9.32-34. Mat. 12.22,24.\x*.
\v 16 Labanye be\add m\add*linga\x + Joha. 8.6.\x* badinga kuye isibonakaliso esivela ezulwini\x + 11.29. Mat. 12.38.\x*.
\v 17 Kodwa yena eyazi imicabango yabo wathi kubo\x + Mat. 12.25-29. Mark. 3.23-27.\x*: Wonke umbuso owehlukene umelene lawo ngokwawo uyachitheka; njalo indlu emelene lendlu iyadilika.
\v 18 Njalo uba uSathane laye ehlukene emelane laye ngokwakhe, umbuso wakhe uzakuma njani? Ngoba lithi, ngikhupha amadimoni ngoBhelezebhule.
\v 19 Njalo uba mina ngikhupha amadimoni ngoBhelezebhule, amadodana enu akhupha ngobani? Ngakho wona azakuba ngabagwebi benu\x + Mat. 12.27. Seb. 19.13.\x*.
\v 20 Kodwa uba ngikhupha amadimoni ngomunwe kaNkulunkulu, isibili umbuso kaNkulunkulu usufikile kini\x + Eks. 8.19.\x*.
\v 21 Uba isiqhwaga sihlomile silinda owaso umuzi, impahla yaso isekuthuleni\x + Mat. 26.3.\x*;
\v 22 kodwa nxa olamandla kulaso e\add si\add*sukela asinqobe, uyasemuka izikhali zaso ebesithembele kuzo, abesesaba impango yaso\x + Efe. 6.11,13.\x*.
\v 23 Ongelami umelene lami\x + Mat. 12.30.\x*; longabuthi lami\x + Mat. 3.12; 13.30. Luka 12.17,18. Joha. 11.52.\x* uyachithiza\x + Joha. 10.12. 11.52.\x*.
\s Ukuphenduka okungapheleliyo
\p
\v 24 Nxa umoya ongcolileyo esephumile emuntwini, uyahamba adabule indawo ezomileyo, edinga ukuphumula; kodwa engakutholi athi: Ngizabuyela endlini yami engaphuma kuyo;
\v 25 njalo esefikile ayifice ithanyelwe njalo ilungisiwe.
\v 26 Abesehamba azithathele abanye omoya abayisikhombisa ababi kulaye uqobo, bangene bahlale lapho; njalo ukucina kwalowomuntu kube kubi kulokuqala\x + Mat. 12.43-45.\x*.
\p
\v 27 Kwasekusithi ekhuluma lezizinto, owesifazana othile exukwini waphakamisa ilizwi, wathi kuye\x + Seb. 2.14; 14.11; 22.22.\x*: Sibusisiwe isisu esakuthwalayo, lamabele owawamunyayo\x + 1.48. 1.45.\x*.
\v 28 Kodwa yena wathi: Kodwa ikakhulu\x + Roma 9.20; 10.18.\x* babusisiwe\x + Joha. 13.17. Jak. 1.25.\x* abalizwayo ilizwi likaNkulunkulu\x + 8.21.\x* balilondoloze\x + Seb. 7.53. Levi 22.31.\x*.
\s Abafuna isibonakaliso
\p
\v 29 Kwathi sekubuthene amaxuku eminyene, waqala ukuthi: Lesi isizukulwana sibi; sidinga isibonakaliso, kodwa kasiyikunikwa isibonakaliso, ngaphandle kwesibonakaliso sikaJona umprofethi.
\v 30 Ngoba njengalokhu uJona waba yisibonakaliso kwabeNineve, leNdodana yomuntu izakuba njalo kulesisizukulwana\x + Mat. 12.39-42. Luka 11.16.\x*.
\v 31 Indlovukazi yeningizimu izasukuma ekugwetshweni kanye lamadoda alesisizukulwana\x + Mat. 12.42.\x*, iwalahle; ngoba yavela emikhawulweni yomhlaba uku\add zaku\add*zwa inhlakanipho kaSolomoni, njalo khangelani, omkhulu kuloSolomoni ulapha.
\v 32 Amadoda eNineve azasukuma ekugwetshweni kanye lalesisizukulwana\x + Mat. 12.41.\x*, asilahle; ngoba aphenduka ngokutshumayela kukaJona, njalo khangelani, omkhulu kuloJona ulapha.
\s Imifanekiso yezibane
\p
\v 33 Futhi kakho othi eselumathise isibane asibeke ekusithekeni, loba ngaphansi kwesitsha, kodwa phezu kwesiqobane sesibane\x + Mat. 5.15. Mark. 4.21.\x*, ukuze abangenayo babone ukukhanya\x + 8.16.\x*.
\p
\v 34 Isibane somzimba yilihlo; ngakho nxa ilihlo lakho liphilile, lomzimba wakho wonke ugcwele ukukhanya\x + 11.34,35, Mat. 6.22,23.\x*; kodwa nxa lilibi, lomzimba wakho ulobumnyama\x + Mat. 6.23.\x*.
\v 35 Ngakho qaphela ukuthi ukukhanya okukuwe kungabi ngumnyama.
\v 36 Ngakho uba umzimba wakho wonke ugcwele ukukhanya, ungelandawo emnyama, uzakhanya wonke, njengesibane sikukhanyisa ngokukhanya\x + Nah. 3.3.\x*.
\s UJesu usola abaFarisi lezazumlayo
\p
\v 37 Kwathi esakhuluma, umFarisi othile wamcela ukuthi adle laye; wasengena wahlala ekudleni\x + Mat. 22.4.\x*.
\v 38 Kwathi umFarisi ebona \add lokhu\add* wamangala ukuthi kazange aqale ageze\x + Mark. 7.3,4.\x* phambi kokudla kwemini\x + Mat. 22.4.\x*.
\v 39 Yasisithi iNkosi kuye: Khathesi lina baFarisi lihlambulula ingaphandle yenkezo leyesitsha\x + Mat. 23.25.\x*, kodwa ingaphakathi yenu igcwele ukuphanga lobubi\x + Mat. 23.25.\x*.
\v 40 Zithutha, yena owenza ingaphandle kayenzanga yini lengaphakathi?
\v 41 Kodwa phanini zibe yizipho zabayanga lezozinto ezingaphakathi\x + 12.33. 16.9. 3.11. 16.14.\x*; khangelani-ke, konke kuzahlambuluka kini\x + Tit. 1.15.\x*.
\p
\v 42 Kodwa maye kini baFarisi\x + Mat. 23.23.\x*! Ngoba lithela okwetshumi kwetshwayi leganga \w leruwi\w**, lakuyo yonke imibhida, njalo liseqa ukwehlulela lothando lukaNkulunkulu; belifanele ukwenza lezizinto, lingakuyekeli lalokhu\x + 18.12.\x*.
\p
\v 43 Maye kini baFarisi! Ngoba lithanda izihlalo zabahloniphekayo emasinagogeni\x + Mat. 23.6. Mark. 12.39 Luka 20.46.\x*, lokubingelelwa emidangeni\x + Mat. 23.7. Mark. 12.38 Luka 20.46.\x*.
\p
\v 44 Maye kini, babhali labaFarisi, bazenzisi! Ngoba lifanana lamangcwaba angabonakaliyo, labantu abahamba phezu kwawo bengawazi\x + Mat. 23.27.\x*.
\p
\v 45 Omunye wezazumthetho wasephendula wathi kuye: Mfundisi, ngokutsho lezizinto uyasithuka lathi\x + 11.46,52. Mat. 22.35.\x*.
\v 46 Kodwa wathi: Maye lakini zazumthetho\x + 11.46,52. Mat. 22.35.\x*! Ngoba\x + Mat. 23.4.\x* lethwesa abantu imithwalo enzima ukuthwalwa, kodwa lina uqobo lwenu kaliyithinti leyomithwalo \add la\add*ngomunye weminwe yenu\x + Mat. 11.28.\x*.
\p
\v 47 Maye kini! Ngoba lakha amangcwaba abaprofethi, njalo oyihlo bababulala\x + Mat. 23.29-31.\x*.
\v 48 Ngalokhu-ke lifakaza\x + Mat. 23.29-31.\x* ukuthi livumelana lemisebenzi yaboyihlo; ngoba bona bababulala, lina-ke liyawakha amangcwaba abo\x + Roma 1.32.\x*.
\v 49 Ngalokhu-ke inhlakanipho kaNkulunkulu yathi\x + 1 Kor. 1.24. Zaga 8.12,22,23,30. Kol. 2.3. Mat. 23.34.\x*: Ngizabathuma abaprofethi labaphostoli\x + Mat. 23.34-36. 2 Lan. 24.19. 36.15,16.\x*, la\add banye\add* babo bazababulala ba\add ba\add*xotshe\x + 1 Thes. 2.15. Mat. 23.34.\x*;
\v 50 ukuze kubizwe kulesisizukulwana igazi labaprofethi bonke elachithwa kusukela ekusekelweni komhlaba\x + Mat. 13.35.\x*,
\v 51 kusukela egazini likaAbela kuze kufike egazini likaZakariya owabulawa phakathi laphakathi kwelathi lendlu \add kaNkulunkulu\add*; yebo, ngithi kini: Lizabizwa kulesisizukulwana\x + Mat. 23.35.\x*.
\p
\v 52 Maye kini zazumthetho\x + 11.46,52. Mat. 22.35.\x*! Ngoba lisusile\x + Mat. 23.13.\x* isihluthulelo solwazi; kalingenanga lina uqobo lwenu\x + 1.77. Roma 2.20.\x*, labangenayo labavimbela.
\p
\v 53 Kwathi ekhuluma lezizinto kubo, ababhali labaFarisi baqala uku\add m\add*ngxamela kakhulukazi, lokumbuzisisa ngezinto ezinengi\x + Mark. 6.19.\x*,
\v 54 bemthiya\x + Seb. 23.21.\x*, bedinga ukubamba ulutho oluphuma emlonyeni wakhe\x + Mat. 22.15. Mark. 12.13.\x*, ukuze bambeke icala\x + Mat. 12.10. Mark. 3.2. Joha. 8.6.\x*.